iew-title\">Better than Shopify!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/notblowingsmoke/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25f9d674b5deb80ecdf6800e933f3dc9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/25f9d674b5deb80ecdf6800e933f3dc9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/notblowingsmoke/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">E-Liquids UK <small>(notblowingsmoke)</small></a> <span class=\"review-date\">7 октября, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce has carried our business since 2016, the extendability and reliability of the core plugin has allowed us to build a thriving ecommerce business. There are a lot of features which should be in the core plugin but those are easily added through the many premium plugins.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve used WooCommerce for years and have no reason to change. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Duplicate orders</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kavitharamar/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/32b8c23945f3ff2d83bc86a230dce017?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/32b8c23945f3ff2d83bc86a230dce017?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kavitharamar/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kavitharamar</a> <span class=\"review-date\">7 октября, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are developing a site using woocommerce. We are about to finish the development, now the problem is the orders are duplicated with different order id and have receiving 2 emails and 2 sms notifications for the same order. Also the payments are asking to pay twice for the already partially paid order. Seeing the logs on Woocommerrce&gt; status&gt;logs, we received \"Transactional email triggered fatal error for callback woocommerce_email_order_meta\". Sometimes, the orders appeared to be 1 time, most of the times , the orders are duplicated. Also when we see the orders on Woocommerce&gt;orders , the duplicate orders with different order id  appears to be completed and when we see the orders on pending payments, the duplicate orders with different order id  appears to be in pending payment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thanks for helping me troubleshoot a PHP conflict</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/glazergallery/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/930cab831e7539e267d92538adb9cfa4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/930cab831e7539e267d92538adb9cfa4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/glazergallery/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">glazergallery</a> <span class=\"review-date\">4 октября, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I appreciate the troubleshooting suggestions I got from this forum recently that helped me to locate the source of a conflict with PHP 8 that had not shown up with earlier PHP versions. (It was in my custom code in my Child Theme that we actually no longer need anyway.) Our retail shop has been using WooCommerce for almost 8 years with a Site Origin theme, and have found that combination to be flexible, stable, and customizable. A big plus is that the non-technical people on staff can easily learn to add, remove, and update product pages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Horrible Documentation</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/websitende/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/03b3b4a067514e284b0421790187d3cc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/03b3b4a067514e284b0421790187d3cc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/websitende/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">websitende</a> <span class=\"review-date\">3 октября, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not a designer? Want to know how to work with Woo and its plug-ins? Well, forget it. HORRIBLE documentation. The only place I get any help is from the FB group WPbeginner. Thank goodness for them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Punctual and attentive support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 из 5 звезд\" data-title-template=\"%s из 5 звезд\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-fil